title: Did U.S. Rep. Ocasio-Cortez Repeatedly Guess ‘Free’ on TV Show ‘The Price is Right?’
subtitle: Might be hard to "come on down" to "The Price is Right" if that's your only response.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Congresswoman Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez repeatedly guessed "free" in response to questions during an appearance on the game show "The Price is Right."
